# Tip
You Should stop seeing perticular direction if you came across any gaurd or wall

# Approach
<!-- Describe your approach to solving the problem. -->
if gaurd ==> cell be 1;
if wall ==> cell be 2;
if the cell can be seen by any gaurd then ==> cell be 3;
you can check that by looping through all the four directions

At the end the answer will be no of cells with "-1".

