# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->
going from left to right, if there is wall on right side of guard then elements after that are not guarded

going from  right to left , if there is wall on left side of guard then elements after that are not guarded

going from  top to down , if there is wall on down side of guard then elements down to that are not guarded

going from  down to top , if there is wall on top side of guard then elements top to that are not guarded


# Code
