* the quetion it is to find the minimum time ,and given that can fill 2 at a time or 1 
* to find minimum first fill how many times 2 cups can be filled using priority queue(filling last maximum 2 cups) and remaining will be a left out cup fill it directly with that value.

```
class Solution {
    public int fillCups(int[] nums) {
        int c=0,t1=0,t2=0;
        PriorityQueue<Integer>q=new PriorityQueue<>(Collections.reverseOrder());
         for(int i:nums)
             q.add(i);
        while(q.peek()!=0){
            t1=q.remove();
            t2=q.remove();
            if(t2!=0){
                q.add(t1-1);
                q.add(t2-1);
                c++;
            }
            else return c+t1;
        }
        return c;
    }
}
```

